Enrollment Rules
One Enrollment Per Course

A student cannot own the same course twice.

The system enforces:

unique(student, course)

This prevents:

Duplicate purchases
Duplicate enrollments
Data inconsistency
Enrollment Activation

Each enrollment contains:

is_active

Purpose:

Allow disabling access later without deleting records

Example future uses:

